      *        * Sub-saldo 1                                           *
      *        *-------------------------------------------------------*
           05  d-sld-mag-sub-s01          pic s9(08)v9(03) sign is
                                                           trailing
                                                           separate
                                                           character  .
      *        *-------------------------------------------------------*
      *        * Sub-saldo 2                                           *
      *        *-------------------------------------------------------*
           05  d-sld-mag-sub-s02          pic s9(08)v9(03) sign is
                                                           trailing
                                                           separate
                                                           character  .
      *        *-------------------------------------------------------*
      *        * Sub-saldo 3                                           *
      *        *-------------------------------------------------------*
           05  d-sld-mag-sub-s03          pic s9(08)v9(03) sign is
                                                           trailing
                                                           separate
                                                           character  .
      *        *-------------------------------------------------------*
      *        * Sub-saldo 4                                           *
      *        *-------------------------------------------------------*
           05  d-sld-mag-sub-s04          pic s9(08)v9(03) sign is
                                                           trailing
                                                           separate
                                                           character  .
      *        *-------------------------------------------------------*
      *        * Sub-saldo 5                                           *
      *        *-------------------------------------------------------*
           05  d-sld-mag-sub-s05          pic s9(08)v9(03) sign is
                                                           trailing
